## Query (D) — Customers who purchased Pratchett books and the titles they bought

```sql
SELECT DISTINCT c.first_name || ' ' || c.last_name AS customer, b.title
FROM CUSTOMER c
JOIN ORDERS o ON c.customer_id = o.customer_id
JOIN ORDER_ITEM oi ON o.order_id = oi.order_id
JOIN BOOK b ON oi.book_id = b.book_id
JOIN BOOK_AUTHOR ba ON b.book_id = ba.book_id
JOIN AUTHOR a ON ba.author_id = a.author_id
WHERE (a.first_name || ' ' || a.last_name) LIKE '%Pratchett%'
ORDER BY customer, b.title;
